            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Valerius <lb n="2"/>Luci<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> centiri<lb break="no" n="3"/>on <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>legi</abbr><ex>onis</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>Fla</abbr><ex>viae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Macedon stu<lb break="no" n="5"/>pendi&amp;lt;h&amp;gt;oron <note>sic</note> X <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>fe</abbr><ex>cit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dul</abbr><ex>cissimo</ex></expan> frater <lb n="7"/>Limeni<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>frater sehr wahrscheinlich als Kommilitone, nicht als Bruder zu verstehen. (B): Sartori: Valerius / Iucis(?) centiri/on leg(ionis) (quartae) Fla(viae) / Macedon stu/pendihoron (decem) / fe(cit?) dul(cis?) frater / Limenis.</p>
            </div>
